extends layout

block content
  .container
    .hero-unit
      h1 uva: a RunKeeper Calendar
      p RunKeeper's Activity display is heavily focused on chronological ordering and a 'feed' view. For those of us who pride ourselves in "Don't break the streak"-style mentalities, it's often better to see things laid out visually, across a calendar.
      a(href='/runkeeper_login')
        img(src='http://static1.runkeeper.com/images/assets/login-blue-white-300x57.png')
    .row
      .col-md-6
        h2 resources
        p uva could never have been created without the following filler text:
        p Lo-fi thundercats beard tumblr. Bicycle rights before they sold out vinyl terry richardson keytar blog, artisan viral iphone wolf whatever beard. Twee gluten-free sartorial 8-bit viral. High life sustainable cardigan food truck seitan, banh mi banksy tumblr organic +1. Lo-fi PBR salvia jean shorts.
        ul
          li: a(href='http://runkeeper.com/partner/applications') Application Portal
          li: a(href='http://developer.runkeeper.com/healthgraph') RunKeeper Health Graph API
          li: a(href='http://groups.google.com/group/HealthGraph') Health Graph Google Group
      .col-md-6
        h2 a sneak peek
        ul.media-grid
          li
            img.thumbnail(src='images/preview.png')
      .col-md-4
        h2 built gratefully with
        p
